Ing '''Indu ning Alang Anggang Saup'''  ({{lang-la|Nostra Mater de Perpetuo Succursu}}), a '''Our Mother of Perpetual Help''', '''Our Lady of Perpetual Help''', o '''Our Lady of Perpetual Succour''')<ref group="Note">The [[Catholic Encyclopedia]] of 1913 uses the latter name, but the former is more prevalent today.  It is officially known in Latin as '''Mater de Perpetuo Succursu''' (Mother of Perpetual Succour/Help).</ref> king Ingles, metung yang Catolicung titulung binye nang [[Papa Pio IX]]. Makaugne ya king bantug a imaheng [[Byzantine art|Bizantino]]ng pareu lagyung ibat kanitang ka-15ng dilanwa o siglu.

Atyu ne king [[Roma]] manibat anyang 1499, at permanenti yang makabili king [[Church of St. Alphonsus Liguori, Rome|pisamban nang Sant'Alfonso di Liguori]] king [[Talimunduk a Esquiline ]]. King [[Pisambang Aslagang Orthodox]], ing aus da king imaheng iti, ''Virgin of the Passion'' o ''[[Theotokos]] of the Passion'' uling kareng arkanghel a makapadurut king imahe.  
 
